📊 Analytics Project Ideas for NHS 

1️⃣ Elective Recovery & Waiting List Modelling 

Forecast RTT (Referral-to-Treatment) waiting lists using regression/time-series. 

Identify bottlenecks in specialties exceeding 18-week standard. 

Predict impact of adding clinical capacity on backlog clearance. 

Why relevant: NHS aims to have 65% seen within 18 weeks and reduce long waits. 

 

2️⃣  Virtual Wards & Remote Monitoring Impact Evaluation 

Analyse patient outcomes for virtual ward admissions. 

Estimate avoided admissions and cost savings. 

Why relevant: NHS guidance pushes digital tools and remote care to reduce pressures. 

 

